snippet.textDisplay:
The description has *most of the translation, except this verse*: Please! I'll try but correct my mistakes! Thx!

Chaand teri roshni,aftaab se hai magar,
Oh moon, your light is as bright as the sun, but...

Chaah ke bhi na mile hai, dono ki nazar
Even desiring those two lights, am unable to see them

aasmaan ye mera jaane, dono kab hain mile
The sky knows when I will find the two ?

Duriyaan, din raat ki hein,tai na ho fasle
Day and night are so far apart, I can't bridge that distance

Benaam si khwaishein,aawaz na mile
Unspoken wishes, go unheard......
